---
// src/components/MythBusterFlip.astro
// UX UPGRADED: Pure Corporate Authority with Clear Call-to-Action (No Sci-Fi)
---

<section class="relative w-full py-24 bg-[#0a0f1c] border-t border-slate-800/80 font-sans overflow-hidden" id="myth-buster-section">
  
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.01)_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.01)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:32px_32px] pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 lg:px-8 max-w-7xl relative z-10">
    
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center mb-16">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2 rounded-full bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-6 shadow-sm">
        <span class="text-slate-400">Industry Clarification Protocol</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-serif text-white font-medium leading-[1.15] tracking-tight mb-6">
        Declassifying the <br class="hidden md:block"/>
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-400 to-amber-200 font-bold">Great MBBS Illusions.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg font-medium leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Unethical contractors thrive on your lack of information. Tap the button on any card below to flip it and reveal the verified reality.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 perspective-1000">
      
      <div class="flip-card group w-full h-[420px] cursor-pointer">
        <div class="flip-card-inner relative w-full h-full transition-transform duration-[800ms] preserve-3d">
          
          <div class="flip-card-front absolute w-full h-full backface-hidden bg-[#121826] border border-slate-700/80 rounded-[2rem] p-8 flex flex-col shadow-[0_15px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.3)] transition-colors group-hover:border-slate-500">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-rose-500/10 border border-rose-500/30 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-rose-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 11V9a2 2 0 00-2-2m2 4v4a2 2 0 104 0v-1m-4-3H9m2 0h4m6 1a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-rose-400 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Common Pitch #1</span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-slate-200 italic leading-snug mb-auto">
              "We guarantee 100% MBBS in a top European University for just ₹15 Lakhs total."
            </h3>
            
            <div class="mt-8 w-full bg-slate-800/80 group-hover:bg-slate-700 border border-slate-600 rounded-xl py-4 flex items-center justify-center gap-3 transition-colors shadow-sm">
              <span class="text-slate-200 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Flip to Reveal Truth</span>
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-400 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" /></svg>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flip-card-back absolute w-full h-full backface-hidden rotate-y-180 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-950 to-[#030712] border border-emerald-500/40 rounded-[2rem] p-8 flex flex-col shadow-[0_20px_40px_rgba(16,185,129,0.15)]">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/20 border border-emerald-500/50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" /></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-emerald-400 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">The Finesse Reality</span>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-white leading-snug mb-4">
              The ₹12L Hidden Contractor Trap.
            </h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 relative z-10 mb-auto">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-300">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 mt-1.5 shrink-0"></div>
                No 'Top' university costs ₹15L total.
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-300">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 mt-1.5 shrink-0"></div>
                Contractors artificially deflate 1st-year fees to lure you in.
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-emerald-100 font-bold bg-emerald-500/10 px-3 py-2 rounded-lg border border-emerald-500/20">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-400 mt-1.5 shrink-0"></div>
                Finesse ensures 100% Direct Billing to the University.
              </li>
            </ul>
            
            <div class="mt-8 text-center border-t border-emerald-500/20 pt-4">
              <span class="text-emerald-500/70 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                <svg class="w-3 h-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18" /></svg>
                Tap to close report
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flip-card group w-full h-[420px] cursor-pointer">
        <div class="flip-card-inner relative w-full h-full transition-transform duration-[800ms] preserve-3d">
          
          <div class="flip-card-front absolute w-full h-full backface-hidden bg-[#121826] border border-slate-700/80 rounded-[2rem] p-8 flex flex-col shadow-[0_15px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.3)] transition-colors group-hover:border-slate-500">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-amber-500/10 border border-amber-500/30 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5h12M9 3v2m1.048 9.5A18.022 18.022 0 016.412 9m6.088 9h7M11 21l5-10 5 10M12.751 5C11.783 10.77 8.07 15.61 3 18.129" /></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-amber-400 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Common Pitch #2</span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-slate-200 italic leading-snug mb-auto">
              "Bilingual courses (English + Russian) are easy and perfectly valid for India."
            </h3>
            
            <div class="mt-8 w-full bg-slate-800/80 group-hover:bg-slate-700 border border-slate-600 rounded-xl py-4 flex items-center justify-center gap-3 transition-colors shadow-sm">
              <span class="text-slate-200 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Flip to Reveal Truth</span>
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-400 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" /></svg>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flip-card-back absolute w-full h-full backface-hidden rotate-y-180 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-950 to-[#030712] border border-emerald-500/40 rounded-[2rem] p-8 flex flex-col shadow-[0_20px_40px_rgba(16,185,129,0.15)]">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/20 border border-emerald-500/50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" /></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-emerald-400 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">The Finesse Reality</span>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-white leading-snug mb-4">
              Instant NMC Disqualification.
            </h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 relative z-10 mb-auto">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-300">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 mt-1.5 shrink-0"></div>
                NMC 2021 Gazette explicitly states the course MUST be in English.
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-300">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 mt-1.5 shrink-0"></div>
                3rd-year clinicals in Russian lead to massive FMGE failure.
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-emerald-100 font-bold bg-emerald-500/10 px-3 py-2 rounded-lg border border-emerald-500/20">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-400 mt-1.5 shrink-0"></div>
                We only map 100% English Mandated universities.
              </li>
            </ul>
            
            <div class="mt-8 text-center border-t border-emerald-500/20 pt-4">
              <span class="text-emerald-500/70 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                <svg class="w-3 h-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18" /></svg>
                Tap to close report
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flip-card group w-full h-[420px] cursor-pointer">
        <div class="flip-card-inner relative w-full h-full transition-transform duration-[800ms] preserve-3d">
          
          <div class="flip-card-front absolute w-full h-full backface-hidden bg-[#121826] border border-slate-700/80 rounded-[2rem] p-8 flex flex-col shadow-[0_15px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.3)] transition-colors group-hover:border-slate-500">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/30 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M12 14l9-5-9-5-9 5 9 5z" /><path d="M12 14l6.16-3.422a12.083 12.083 0 01.665 6.479A11.952 11.952 0 0012 20.055a11.952 11.952 0 00-6.824-2.998 12.078 12.078 0 01.665-6.479L12 14z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" /></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-blue-400 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Common Pitch #3</span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-slate-200 italic leading-snug mb-auto">
              "You have scored well. We can get you a 50% Scholarship in Russia."
            </h3>
            
            <div class="mt-8 w-full bg-slate-800/80 group-hover:bg-slate-700 border border-slate-600 rounded-xl py-4 flex items-center justify-center gap-3 transition-colors shadow-sm">
              <span class="text-slate-200 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Flip to Reveal Truth</span>
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-400 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" /></svg>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flip-card-back absolute w-full h-full backface-hidden rotate-y-180 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-950 to-[#030712] border border-emerald-500/40 rounded-[2rem] p-8 flex flex-col shadow-[0_20px_40px_rgba(16,185,129,0.15)]">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/20 border border-emerald-500/50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" /></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-emerald-400 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">The Finesse Reality</span>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-white leading-snug mb-4">
              The Fake Discount Gimmick.
            </h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 relative z-10 mb-auto">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-300">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 mt-1.5 shrink-0"></div>
                Sovereign universities DO NOT offer MBBS scholarships to foreigners.
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-300">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 mt-1.5 shrink-0"></div>
                The "discount" is just their inflated commission being reduced.
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-emerald-100 font-bold bg-emerald-500/10 px-3 py-2 rounded-lg border border-emerald-500/20">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-400 mt-1.5 shrink-0"></div>
                Finesse provides a fixed, transparent fee structure from Day 1.
              </li>
            </ul>
            
            <div class="mt-8 text-center border-t border-emerald-500/20 pt-4">
              <span class="text-emerald-500/70 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                <svg class="w-3 h-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18" /></svg>
                Tap to close report
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .perspective-1000 { perspective: 1000px; }
  .preserve-3d { transform-style: preserve-3d; }
  .backface-hidden { backface-visibility: hidden; -webkit-backface-visibility: hidden; }
  .rotate-y-180 { transform: rotateY(180deg); }
  .flip-card.flipped .flip-card-inner { transform: rotateY(180deg); }
</style>

<script is:inline>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    const cards = document.querySelectorAll('.flip-card');
    
    cards.forEach(card => {
      card.addEventListener('click', () => {
        card.classList.toggle('flipped');
      });
    });
  });
</script>